						<div class="caption richtextContent">
	<p>On Oct. 27, 2020,&nbsp;Denise Balkissoon, executive editor of Chatelaine, gave the 2020 Atkinson Lecture. She spoke about the concept of objectivity—whether it's possible, whether it's useful, and what role it plays in keeping certain stories untold.</p>
